metadata.name: Tamtaro Excluded SEL Only
metadata.description: This template imports only the excluded stream expressions (SEL v2.5.1). Designed for those who want high-quality results with minimal clutter. Will not overwrite anything else in your current AIOStreaams. Just click Skip debrid credentials screen during Template Import.
metadata.author: Tamtaro
